data.name: Gala Apple Snack Platter
data.quickTastyDescription: A refreshing and colorful snack platter featuring sweet Gala apples paired with delicious dips and toppings for a perfect snack.
detailedCookingInstructions: Wash and slice the Gala apples into wedges, removing the core.
Arrange the apple wedges on a platter.
In a small bowl, mix peanut butter and honey until smooth.
Serve the peanut butter dip in a small bowl on the platter, allowing for easy dipping.
Sprinkle cinnamon over the apple wedges for added flavor.
Scatter granola and dark chocolate chips around the platter for a crunchy and sweet topping.
